            • com.tectonica.jonix.export.JonixTabDelimitedExporter<H,P>

  • public class JonixTabDelimitedExporter<H,P>
extends JonixExporter<H,P>
    An exporter for generating tab-delimited output out of ONIX source(s). Turning a tree-like ONIX product into a fixed-length column-oriented table is far from trivial. All the details are explained in JonixColumn.
    Author:
    Zach Melamed
